# Sentiment Analysis on Cars.com (R)
# Programmatically download and analysed live car reviews using NLP. Compute sentiment analysis of each review using AFFIN index and
# predict the customer rating based on it using Decision Trees and Random Forest. 
# Computed and Visualized top words with TF-IDF scores and provide it to manufacturers to take necessary action for future manufacturing.


1) Run the code in R-Studio and run the app
2) The URL is defaulted to https://www.cars.com/research/toyota-camry/ 
